               <msContents>
                  <summary>Missal. F<locus target="#1r"/>-84: Supplications, Mästäbqwu‘ǝ, መስተብቍዕ፡ (some folios are missing between ff. 7 and 8). F<locus target="#8r"/>-15v: Liton. (some folios are missing between f<locus target="#13"/> and 14). F<locus target="#14r"/>-20v Salota Kidan, incomplete at the beginning. F<locus target="#20v"/>-22v. Starting of the Liturgy. F<locus target="#47r"/>-59v: Anaphora of the Apostles, Qǝddase Ḫawaryat, ቅዳሴ፡ ሐዋርያት፡. F<locus target="#59v"/>-65v: Anaphora of Our Lord, ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእ፡.  F<locus target="#65v"/>-75v: Anaphora of John Chrysostom, Qǝddase Yoḥannǝs Afä Wärq, ቅዳሴ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ አፈወርቅ፡. F<locus target="#75v"/>-93r: Anaphora of John, Son of Thunder, Qǝddase Yoḥannǝs Wäldä Nägwädǝgwad, ቅዳሴ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ነጐድጓድ፡. F<locus target="#93r"/>-110v: Anaphora of Our Lady Mary attributed to Cyriacus of Bǝhǝnsa, Qǝddase Maryam Gwäs’a, ቅዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡. F<locus target="#110v"/>-115r: Anaphora of Dioscorus, Qǝddase Diosǝqoros, ቅዳሴ፡ ዲዮስቆሮስ፡. <locus target="#115v"/>: unidentified text in a later hand.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="115r" facs="001"/><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1960Mashaf">Maṣḥafa qǝddāse</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="8r" facs="001"/><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4711Mastabqwe">Mastabqʷǝʿān</title><note>Some folios are missing between <locus target="#7 #8" facs="008"/></note></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="8r" to="15v" facs="008"/><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3188Liton">Liṭon</title><note>Some folios are missing between <locus target="#13 #14" facs="014"/></note></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from="14r" to="20v" facs="014"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2260salota">Ṣalota kidān</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from="20v" to="47r" facs="021"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1960Mashaf#SerataQeddase">Maṣḥafa qǝddāse, Śǝrʿāta qǝddāseሥርዓተ፡ ቅዳሴ፡</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5"><locus from="47r" to="59v" facs="047"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1960Mashaf#AnaphoraApostles">Maṣḥafa qǝddāse, Anaphora of the Apostlesቅዳሴ፡ ዘሐዋርያት፡ (same as https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1104Anapho)</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6"><locus from="59v" to="65v" facs="060"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1100Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān za-ʾǝgziʾǝna ʾIyasus Krǝstos</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7"><locus from="65v" to="75v" facs="066"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3120Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān za-Yoḥannǝs ʾAfa Warq</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8"><locus from="75v" to="93r" facs="076"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1570habeka">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān za-qǝddus Yoḥannǝs wangelāwi</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9"><locus from="93r" to="110v" facs="093"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1099Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān za-qǝddus Hǝryāqos za-hagara Bǝhnǝsā</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10"><locus from="110v" to="115r" facs="111"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3180Anapho">Anaphora by Dioscorus of Alexandria</title></msItem>
              </msItem>
